FoodsIdea opens you to a new world of recipes. By using a new Home Page we will direct you to an endless world of food ideas.

Make FoodsIdea your Home Page and you'll never need to rack your brain again with what to cook for dinner.

By clicking the “Add To Chrome”, I accept and agree to installing the "Foodsidea" extension and setting Chrome™ New Tab to that provided by the service, setting New Tab searches to Bing, the Terms Of Use (https://www.foodsidea.com/terms.html) and the Privacy Policy.

This extension configures your Home Page to Foodsidea to provide these features content.
The extension provides custom web search and quick links to recipe sites from the new tab.

For other support or to provide feedback, please visit us at https://www.foodsidea.com/contact.html.

Permissions Requested :
"Read and change your data on a number of websites"
For our product to work, we require access to the websites we own and manage.
